yiterator.offsetexists-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ArrayIterator::valid()} - Check whether array contains more entries</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
 * 
     * Check if offset exists
     * @link https://php.net/manual/zh/arrayiterator.offsetexists.php
