bool</a></span>。 </td></tr>     </tbody>       </table>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-arrayiterator.uksort-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ArrayIterator::asort()} - Sort entries by values</span></li>    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ArrayIterator::ksort()} - Sort entries by keys</span></li>    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ArrayIterator::natcasesort()} - Sort entries naturally, case insensitive</span></li>    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ArrayIterator::natsort()} - Sort entries naturally</span></li>    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link ArrayIterator::uasort()} - Sort with a user-defined comparison function and maintain index association</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link uksort()} - 使用用户自定义的比较函数对数组中的键名进行排序</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
